name: Object Labrinth
description:
Object Labrinth is a game where you are trapped within a Labrinth and have to use objects provided to you to proceed

It uses scratch 3.0 and will have .exe files for those who want to try it whenever they want without having to open up their web browser. Us 2 developers are working hard on it and hope you appreciate the demos, prototypes, and betas we provide
